    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "s4a-modules-note",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 879,
      "width": 740,
      "height": 120.0,
      "text": "S4a 2026-07-17: new auth/gateway-keys-service.ts (mint/list/revoke/verify, sha256-at-rest,\ngateway_keys collection) + routes/gateway-keys.ts (/api/v1/gateway-keys, self-service) +\nshared/gateway-keys.ts descriptors. llm/gateway takes verifyGatewayKey as an INJECTED seam from\nserver.ts (llm/ never imports auth/); billing/rate-caps gains the per-key window.",
      "originalText": "S4a 2026-07-17: new auth/gateway-keys-service.ts (mint/list/revoke/verify, sha256-at-rest,\ngateway_keys collection) + routes/gateway-keys.ts (/api/v1/gateway-keys, self-service) +\nshared/gateway-keys.ts descriptors. llm/gateway takes verifyGatewayKey as an INJECTED seam from\nserver.ts (llm/ never imports auth/); billing/rate-caps gains the per-key window.",
      "fontSize": 24,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1e40af",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
