    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "annot-voice-c1-20260718",
      "x": 70,
      "y": 1040,
      "width": 760,
      "height": 190,
      "text": "AS-BUILT 2026-07-18 (voice relay, mega-run C1): voice/ joins tier 3 as streaming/'s SIBLING\nWS carve-out, wired by server.ts (attachVoiceServer) beside attachCanvasServer. Two upgrade\nsurfaces: WS /api/voice/stream (16 kHz linear16 PCM binary up; interim/final transcript +\nutterance_end JSON down, utterance_end_ms client-configurable) and WS /api/voice/tts-stream\n({say,lang} control up; audio frames down; {clear} aborts synthesis - the barge-in path).\nAuth: platform session JWT ?token= through verifySseToken (CONV-1, fail closed). Per\nconnection: org+user attribution on every provider call record, 10-min inactivity timeout,\nper-stage latency JSON (audio_in_first/first_interim/utterance_end/tts_first_audio). Vendor-\nneutral SttProvider/TtsProvider registry behind config keys (en=deepgram-aura2, pt=google,\nfallback=elevenlabs); v1 registers STUBS only - live vendors land at C6. Wire shapes:\nshared/src/voice.ts. NOT model egress: voice/ never imports llm/.",
      "originalText": "AS-BUILT 2026-07-18 (voice relay, mega-run C1): voice/ joins tier 3 as streaming/'s SIBLING\nWS carve-out, wired by server.ts (attachVoiceServer) beside attachCanvasServer. Two upgrade\nsurfaces: WS /api/voice/stream (16 kHz linear16 PCM binary up; interim/final transcript +\nutterance_end JSON down, utterance_end_ms client-configurable) and WS /api/voice/tts-stream\n({say,lang} control up; audio frames down; {clear} aborts synthesis - the barge-in path).\nAuth: platform session JWT ?token= through verifySseToken (CONV-1, fail closed). Per\nconnection: org+user attribution on every provider call record, 10-min inactivity timeout,\nper-stage latency JSON (audio_in_first/first_interim/utterance_end/tts_first_audio). Vendor-\nneutral SttProvider/TtsProvider registry behind config keys (en=deepgram-aura2, pt=google,\nfallback=elevenlabs); v1 registers STUBS only - live vendors land at C6. Wire shapes:\nshared/src/voice.ts. NOT model egress: voice/ never imports llm/.",
      "rawText": "AS-BUILT 2026-07-18 (voice relay, mega-run C1): voice/ joins tier 3 as streaming/'s SIBLING\nWS carve-out, wired by server.ts (attachVoiceServer) beside attachCanvasServer. Two upgrade\nsurfaces: WS /api/voice/stream (16 kHz linear16 PCM binary up; interim/final transcript +\nutterance_end JSON down, utterance_end_ms client-configurable) and WS /api/voice/tts-stream\n({say,lang} control up; audio frames down; {clear} aborts synthesis - the barge-in path).\nAuth: platform session JWT ?token= through verifySseToken (CONV-1, fail closed). Per\nconnection: org+user attribution on every provider call record, 10-min inactivity timeout,\nper-stage latency JSON (audio_in_first/first_interim/utterance_end/tts_first_audio). Vendor-\nneutral SttProvider/TtsProvider registry behind config keys (en=deepgram-aura2, pt=google,\nfallback=elevenlabs); v1 registers STUBS only - live vendors land at C6. Wire shapes:\nshared/src/voice.ts. NOT model egress: voice/ never imports llm/.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#b45309",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 47210918,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 815263105,
      "isDeleted": false,
