    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "annot-voice-c5-20260718",
      "x": 70,
      "y": 1260,
      "width": 760,
      "height": 205,
      "text": "AS-BUILT 2026-07-18 (TTS text pipeline + voice context note, mega-run C5): voice/text/ is the\npure text stage INSIDE the relay's tts-stream say path, applied BEFORE the provider:\nsanitizeForSpeech (strip markdown/code/tables/images - belt-and-braces behind the agent-side\nnote) -> normalizeNumbersPt/En (speakable.ts, RELOCATED from web/lib/voice at C5: the pipeline\nis api-side, FIXED-1 forbids cross-imports, shared/ is contract-only - decisions.md) ->\nchunkSentences (abbreviation/number-safe). The relay synthesizes PER SENTENCE, so one say\nstreams N complete WAV containers; the web playback client (web/lib/voice: wav.ts RIFF-length\nsegmentation, playback-queue.ts strict-order queue, tts-playback.ts decoded\nAudioBufferSourceNode per sentence + sync-in-tap unlock + defensive resume; barge-in stops +\nflushes) starts playing at the FIRST completed sentence. agents/context.ts voiceContextNote:\nvoice-sourced turns get a spoken-modality system note (never shortens replies); the client\nsignal wires at C7 via StartChatRunInput.source.",
      "originalText": "AS-BUILT 2026-07-18 (TTS text pipeline + voice context note, mega-run C5): voice/text/ is the\npure text stage INSIDE the relay's tts-stream say path, applied BEFORE the provider:\nsanitizeForSpeech (strip markdown/code/tables/images - belt-and-braces behind the agent-side\nnote) -> normalizeNumbersPt/En (speakable.ts, RELOCATED from web/lib/voice at C5: the pipeline\nis api-side, FIXED-1 forbids cross-imports, shared/ is contract-only - decisions.md) ->\nchunkSentences (abbreviation/number-safe). The relay synthesizes PER SENTENCE, so one say\nstreams N complete WAV containers; the web playback client (web/lib/voice: wav.ts RIFF-length\nsegmentation, playback-queue.ts strict-order queue, tts-playback.ts decoded\nAudioBufferSourceNode per sentence + sync-in-tap unlock + defensive resume; barge-in stops +\nflushes) starts playing at the FIRST completed sentence. agents/context.ts voiceContextNote:\nvoice-sourced turns get a spoken-modality system note (never shortens replies); the client\nsignal wires at C7 via StartChatRunInput.source.",
      "rawText": "AS-BUILT 2026-07-18 (TTS text pipeline + voice context note, mega-run C5): voice/text/ is the\npure text stage INSIDE the relay's tts-stream say path, applied BEFORE the provider:\nsanitizeForSpeech (strip markdown/code/tables/images - belt-and-braces behind the agent-side\nnote) -> normalizeNumbersPt/En (speakable.ts, RELOCATED from web/lib/voice at C5: the pipeline\nis api-side, FIXED-1 forbids cross-imports, shared/ is contract-only - decisions.md) ->\nchunkSentences (abbreviation/number-safe). The relay synthesizes PER SENTENCE, so one say\nstreams N complete WAV containers; the web playback client (web/lib/voice: wav.ts RIFF-length\nsegmentation, playback-queue.ts strict-order queue, tts-playback.ts decoded\nAudioBufferSourceNode per sentence + sync-in-tap unlock + defensive resume; barge-in stops +\nflushes) starts playing at the FIRST completed sentence. agents/context.ts voiceContextNote:\nvoice-sourced turns get a spoken-modality system note (never shortens replies); the client\nsignal wires at C7 via StartChatRunInput.source.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#b45309",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
