    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "annot-voice-c4-20260718",
      "x": 70,
      "y": 1495,
      "width": 780,
      "height": 230,
      "text": "AS-BUILT 2026-07-18 (voice capture chain + mic UI, mega-run C4): the BROWSER half of the\nvoice modality, in web/lib/voice + components/voice. Capture: getUserMedia (echo+noise\nsuppression on; AGC off mobile / on desktop) -> AudioContext at NATIVE rate (iOS locks 48k)\n-> pcm-downsample AudioWorklet (public/voice/, committed) -> 16 kHz linear16 frames + RMS\nlevel -> WS /api/voice/stream (token on the upgrade query). Silero VAD via vad-web WASM,\nassets SELF-HOSTED under public/voice/vendor/ (copy-voice-assets.mjs; CSP 'self').\nsession-driver.ts OWNS the C3 reducer and EXECUTES its effect descriptors (capture/WS/\nspeech-channel/timers all injected - unit-tested with fakes); speech-channel.ts serializes\nreply sentences one say at a time over /api/voice/tts-stream into the C5 TtsPlayback.\nUI: mic button on the chat composer (tap=manual, hold=talking), PT-PT status bar + level\nmeter + send-now escape hatch, one-tap resume after backgrounding; `ouvir` joins the sheet\nfooter's extensible actions (sheet-reader.ts). The dashboard's SECOND WS client surface\nbeside the canvas (both dial the api origin; CSP connect-src carries its ws(s) form).",
      "originalText": "AS-BUILT 2026-07-18 (voice capture chain + mic UI, mega-run C4): the BROWSER half of the\nvoice modality, in web/lib/voice + components/voice. Capture: getUserMedia (echo+noise\nsuppression on; AGC off mobile / on desktop) -> AudioContext at NATIVE rate (iOS locks 48k)\n-> pcm-downsample AudioWorklet (public/voice/, committed) -> 16 kHz linear16 frames + RMS\nlevel -> WS /api/voice/stream (token on the upgrade query). Silero VAD via vad-web WASM,\nassets SELF-HOSTED under public/voice/vendor/ (copy-voice-assets.mjs; CSP 'self').\nsession-driver.ts OWNS the C3 reducer and EXECUTES its effect descriptors (capture/WS/\nspeech-channel/timers all injected - unit-tested with fakes); speech-channel.ts serializes\nreply sentences one say at a time over /api/voice/tts-stream into the C5 TtsPlayback.\nUI: mic button on the chat composer (tap=manual, hold=talking), PT-PT status bar + level\nmeter + send-now escape hatch, one-tap resume after backgrounding; `ouvir` joins the sheet\nfooter's extensible actions (sheet-reader.ts). The dashboard's SECOND WS client surface\nbeside the canvas (both dial the api origin; CSP connect-src carries its ws(s) form).",
      "rawText": "AS-BUILT 2026-07-18 (voice capture chain + mic UI, mega-run C4): the BROWSER half of the\nvoice modality, in web/lib/voice + components/voice. Capture: getUserMedia (echo+noise\nsuppression on; AGC off mobile / on desktop) -> AudioContext at NATIVE rate (iOS locks 48k)\n-> pcm-downsample AudioWorklet (public/voice/, committed) -> 16 kHz linear16 frames + RMS\nlevel -> WS /api/voice/stream (token on the upgrade query). Silero VAD via vad-web WASM,\nassets SELF-HOSTED under public/voice/vendor/ (copy-voice-assets.mjs; CSP 'self').\nsession-driver.ts OWNS the C3 reducer and EXECUTES its effect descriptors (capture/WS/\nspeech-channel/timers all injected - unit-tested with fakes); speech-channel.ts serializes\nreply sentences one say at a time over /api/voice/tts-stream into the C5 TtsPlayback.\nUI: mic button on the chat composer (tap=manual, hold=talking), PT-PT status bar + level\nmeter + send-now escape hatch, one-tap resume after backgrounding; `ouvir` joins the sheet\nfooter's extensible actions (sheet-reader.ts). The dashboard's SECOND WS client surface\nbeside the canvas (both dial the api origin; CSP connect-src carries its ws(s) form).",
